Type: Package
Package: printtree
Title: Print Directory Trees for R Projects and Folders
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Arthur", , "prigasgenthian48@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Prints a compact directory tree for a specified folder.
    Optionally detects common project roots such as RStudio projects (via
    .Rproj files) and R package roots (via DESCRIPTION) and prints the
    tree from the detected root. Designed for quick inspection of project
    structure from the R console.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/PrigasG/printtree
